==Finnish==

===Verb===
'''vittuilla'''

# To fuck with someone (NOT fuck someone!), in the meaning of calling them offensive names, humiliating them or otherwise (intentionally) annoying them. 
#:''Onko sinulla otsaa vittuilla mulle, saatana?'' = Are you having forehead to fuck with me, Satan?

Derived from [[vittu]].

